      <h5>Capital of the Qutb Shahi kingdom, it is considered by many as one of the most magnificent fortress complexes in India. A Light and Sound show is held in the evenings wherein the glorious past of Golconda Fort is narrated with Golconda depicted full of life, glory and grandeur.</h5>
      <div>
